  "quest.03E48CD6E5DB806F.quest_desc": {
    "original": "With more \u00266Archives\u0026r unlocked, it is time to explore the lobby and find the \u0026dEcho of The Wyrmwright\u0026r.\n\nWork with them to unlock the \u0026dDraconic Energy\u0026r upgrade for your \u00266World Engine\u0026r.\n\n\u00267\u0026oYou may teleport directly to this Echo from anywhere in the lobby after meeting them using \u0026e/echo wyrmwright\u00267.",
    "translation": "隨著更多\u00266檔案庫\u0026r的解鎖，是時候探索大廳並找出\u0026d飛龍傳人之回聲\u0026r了。\n\n和這位\u0026d回聲\u0026r協力為你的\u00266世界引擎\u0026r解鎖\u0026d龍族能量\u0026r升級吧。\n\n\u00267\u0026o你可以在初訪這位回聲後，於大廳的任何地方使用下列指令傳送至他身旁：「\u0026e/echo wyrmwright\u00267」。",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 03E48CD6E5DB806F",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
    }
  },
