  "quest.0CE3C7A6DE787371.quest_desc": {
    "original": "This compass points to the location of a \u00263Vault.\n\n\u00267\u0026oThe Compass can be Sneak + Right-clicked when within 256 blocks from the vault to instantly teleport to the entrance!\u0026r",
    "translation": "這個羅盤指向一座\u00263寶庫\u0026r的確切地點。\n\n\u00267\u0026o在寶庫的 256 格內手持羅盤「潛行 + 右鍵」\\n可以快速傳送至寶庫入口！\u0026r",
