  "quest.0F48353EDD296510.quest_desc": {
    "original": "Speak to \u0026dThe Wyrmwright\u0026r once you have crafted the \u0026dResonant Void\u0026r and they will show you how to install this \u00263World Engine Upgrade\u0026r.",
    "translation": "當你合成出了\u0026d迴盪虛空\u0026r後，是時候該回訪\u0026d飛龍傳人\u0026r，並向他學習該如何安裝這項\u00263世界引擎升級\u0026r了。",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 0F48353EDD296510",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
    }
  },
  "quest.14537A63D3BDC09B.quest_desc": {
    "original": "Submitting the blocks required for the \u00263Upgrade\u0026f and claiming its rewards will automatically assemble your team's \u00266World Engine\u0026r.\n\n\u0026eNote\u0026f: Any blocks placed where an upgrade should go will be voided.",
    "translation": "提交該\u00263升級\u0026r所需的方塊並領取該獎勵會自動將它組裝到你們隊伍的\u00266世界引擎\u0026r之中。\n\n\u0026e備註\u0026f：任何放置在該升級所需位置的所有方塊都會被銷毀。",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 14537A63D3BDC09B",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
    }
  },
