  "quest.1F0F37429F1177DF.quest_desc": {
    "original": "With more \u00266Archives\u0026r unlocked, it is time to explore the lobby and find the \u0026dEcho of Twilight\u0026r.\n\nWork with them to unlock the \u00263Twilight Upgrade\u0026r for your \u00266World Engine\u0026r.\n\n\u00267\u0026oYou may teleport directly to this Echo from anywhere in the lobby after meeting them using \u0026e/echo twilight\u00267.",
    "translation": "隨著更多\u00266檔案庫\u0026r的解鎖，是時候探索大廳並找出\u0026d暮光族裔之回聲\u0026r了。\n\n和這位\u0026d回聲\u0026r協力為你的\u00266世界引擎\u0026r解鎖\u00263暮光升級\u0026r吧。\n\n\u00267\u0026o你可以在初訪這位回聲後，於大廳的任何地方使用下列指令傳送至他身旁：「\u0026e/echo twilight\u00267」。",
