  "quest.30902357747A64F1.quest_desc": {
    "original": "With the \u00262Yeti\u0026r defeated, you will have access to 2 new vaults to find.\n\nFound within the upper levels of the \u0026bTwilight Forest\u0026r ring, you can run into a vault of the \u0026aSnow Queen's Castle\u0026r.",
    "translation": "當你擊敗了\u00262雪怪首領\u0026r之後，你現在有著兩座全新寶庫能夠探索。\n\n她會出現於\u0026b暮光森林\u0026r環帶較高處的\u0026a冰雪女王城堡\u0026r之中。",
