  "quest.32653261B16850B3.quest_desc": {
    "original": "Once both the \u0026aSnow Queen\u0026r and the \u00262Hydra\u0026r have been defeated, there is one final vault that unlocks.\n\nThe vault of the \u0026dKnight Phantoms\u0026r will be your final puzzle and fight within the \u0026bTwilight Forest\u0026r ring.",
    "translation": "當\u0026a冰雪女王\u0026r和\u00262九頭蛇\u0026r雙雙被擊敗之後，最終寶庫已被解鎖。\n\n\u0026d幻影騎士\u0026r寶庫將會是你在\u0026b暮光森林\u0026r環帶中經歷的最後一道謎題和最後一場戰鬥。",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 32653261B16850B3",
