  "quest.3DCD6DC36B31EEF4.quest_desc": {
    "original": "With these \u00263World Engine Upgrades\u0026r installed, you feel as though you are finally starting to master the \u00266World Engine\u0026r.\n\nHead back to the \u0026dEcho of Guidance\u0026r to see what comes next and unlock even more \u00266Archives\u0026r!",
    "translation": "當你安裝了這麼多\u00263世界引擎升級\u0026r之後，你感覺你終於開始精通\u00266世界引擎\u0026r了。\n\n返回\u0026d指引嚮導之回聲\u0026r處，看看下一步該做什麼，並解鎖更多的\u00266檔案庫\u0026r吧！",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 3DCD6DC36B31EEF4",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
