  "quest.45BA73F16B7AE681.quest_desc": {
    "original": "Found within lower deepslate, the \u00263Ancient City\u0026r holds a giant portal that can finally be activated, allowing you to defeat the boss within.\n\nUpon entering the portal you will receive a blindness effect that can only be cured by filling your \u0026dSoul Cage\u0026r with mob souls dropped from killing strengthened enemies inside the \u00263Vault\u0026r.\n\n\u0026cYou must hold the \u0026dSoul Cage \u0026cin your offhand to charge it!\n\nOnce you have filled your \u0026dSoul Cage\u0026r, you may start the boss fight by taking the elevator in the starting room.\n\n\u0026eNote\u0026r: Killing mobs with the \u00266Reaper\u0026r enchantment will fill your Cage quicker (+1 per Level)",
    "translation": "在深板岩環帶的較低處，\u00263遠古之城\u0026r之中的巨大傳送門終於能夠被點亮，讓你能夠進去擊敗裡面的頭目。\n\n當你進入傳送門之後，你會受到失明效果的影響。只能透過殺死\u00263寶庫\u0026r內的強大敵人，利用他們的靈魂填滿你的\u0026d靈魂牢籠\u0026r，來逐步減緩失明效果。\n\n\u0026c你必須要將\u0026d靈魂牢籠\u0026c放在你的副手才能收集到靈魂！\n\n當你填滿你的\u0026d靈魂牢籠\u0026r之後，你就可以搭上起始房間之中的電梯開啟頭目戰了。\n\n\u0026e備註\u0026r：使用\u00266收割者\u0026r附魔殺死怪物能夠讓你的牢籠滿的更快。（每等級 +1）",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 45BA73F16B7AE681",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
    }
  },
  "quest.45BA73F16B7AE681.title": {
    "original": "\u00263An Ancient Portal",
    "translation": "\u00263一座遠古傳送門",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 45BA73F16B7AE681",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "none",
      "snbt_value_shape": "string"
    }
  },
