  "quest.4BAD7359CF074014.quest_desc": {
    "original": "Before you can harness the power of the void, you'll need to create a machine to craft on an atomic level.\n\nThe \u0026dAtomic Forge\u0026r is perfect for this, and can craft an ingot strong enough to hold in the void.\n\n\u0026eNote\u0026r: The \u0026dAtomic Forge\u0026r must be powered by the \u0026dEnderic Laser\u0026r.",
    "translation": "在你嘗試駕馭虛空之力之前，你需要一台能夠以原子維度進行合成的機器。\n\n\u0026d原子鍛造廠\u0026r就是一台很適合的機器，它能夠合成出一種足以承受虛空的金屬錠。\n\n\u0026e備註\u0026r：\u0026d原子鍛造廠\u0026r必須透過\u0026d終界雷射\u0026r進行充能。",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 4BAD7359CF074014",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
    }
  },
  "quest.4BAD7359CF074014.title": {
    "original": "Making \u00266Prometheum\u0026r",
    "translation": "製造\u00266普羅米修斯錠\u0026r",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 4BAD7359CF074014",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "none",
      "snbt_value_shape": "string"
    }
  },
  "quest.4D6D066B0855586D.quest_desc": {
    "original": "Within the Ocean ring, there is a creature that has been touched by the void.\n\nGood luck.\n\n\u0026eNote\u0026r: You will need an \u0026dAbyssal Sacrifice\u0026r to activate the altar. The items required to craft it can be acquired from the \u00269Coralssus\u0026r \u0026aGateway of Eternity\u0026r.",
    "translation": "在海洋環帶之中，有著一隻曾被虛空觸碰過的生物。\n\n祝你好運。\n\n\u0026e備註\u0026r：你會需要一個\u0026d深淵祭品\u0026r才能啟動祭壇。用來合成它的物品能夠透過\u00269深淵\u0026r\u0026a傳送門珍珠\u0026r獲得。",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 4D6D066B0855586D",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
