  "quest.6D0C1811DA909BBD.quest_desc": {
    "original": "The \u0026dAncient City Vault\u0026r is filled with loot, but the most important item comes from the boss.\n\n3-4 \u0026bCursium Ingots\u0026r will drop on each kill. These ingots can be transformed into a usable upgrade in the \u00266World Engine\u0026r.",
    "translation": "縱使\u0026d遠古之城寶庫\u0026r中有著大量戰利品，但最重要的物品來自於那裡的頭目。\n\n每次殺死牠都會掉落 3~4 個\u0026b咒靈錠\u0026r。\\n這種金屬錠能夠被轉化為一項可用於\u00266世界引擎\u0026r之中的升級。",
    "context": "chapters/world_engine__tier_4.snbt / quest 6D0C1811DA909BBD",
